How to Draw Animals - G. Vilppu


2 h 53 m 24 s | Audio: aac, 44100 Hz, stereo | Video: mpeg4, yuv420p, 1280x720, 29.97 fps | 1.32GB
Genre: eLearning

In this unique video lesson world renowned artist Glenn Vilppu with teach you a clear, step-by-step approach to draw any animal. You will learn about the large anatomical differences among animals and how drawing animals relates to drawing the figure with a few differences. You will learn how to break down the structure of animals in order to draw confidently and work partially or fully from imagination rather than simply copying. Glenn will additionally do several demonstrations of animal drawing in pencils, pen, and wash so you can analyze the steps and the process in action.
